-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nhm 2, bnh nhn c iu tr bng enoxaparin (6000 IU/ngy trong 30 ngy) v cho thy cc triu chng lm sng gim ng k (Thang o VAS gim t 8 xung 4, p &lt; 0,01). Sau  nattokinase c bt u sau khi ngng s dng enoxaparin, cc triu chng lm sng  thuyn gim hon ton ( p &lt; 0,01)  </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nhm 3, nattokinase (100 mg/ngy trong 30 ngy) c bt u mt ngy sau khi phu thut mch mu v gip thuyn gim hon ton cc triu chng  tt c cc bnh nhn c iu tr ( p &lt; 0,01)</span></li>\n</ul>\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"NHNG LU  QUAN TRNG KHI S DNG VIN UNG NATTO SAFFRON CA M\" tag_name=\"h2\" color=\"#e71e27\" class=\"font-title\"]\n\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Khng dng sn phm Natto Saffron cho i tng l tr em, ph n c thai v ang cho con b. V nguy c lm tan cc mu ng, do , nn ngng s dng trc khi thc hin phu thut.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thn trng khi dng Natto Saffron cho ph n trong giai on hnh kinh, nhng ngi mc tnh trng chm ng mu hoc ang chy mu cp tnh.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngoi ra, cn lu  v cc i tng c nguy c v cc bnh l tim mch lin quan n cc mu ng (nhi mu c tim do to cc mu ng, i tho ng, x va mch, ri lon m mu, tha cn, bo ph) v ngi sau tai bin tc mch  n nh s dng  gip phng nga bnh l lin quan n cc mu ng v tng cng sc khe tim mch.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tnh trng ri lon chy mu: Nattokinase c th lm cho tnh trng ri lon chy mu tr nn ti t hn. Do , cn s dng mt cch cn thn.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tht thn trng khi dng sn phm ny trn i tng huyt p thp.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Lu  khi chun b c phu thut: Nattokinase c th lm tng kh nng chy mu qu nhiu trong hoc sau phu thut. Ngoi ra, sn phm cng c th lm cho huyt p kh kim sot trong qu trnh phu 