u sau khi ngng s dng enoxaparin, cc triu chng lm sng  thuyn gim hon ton ( p &lt; 0,01)  </span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nhm 3, nattokinase (100 mg/ngy trong 30 ngy) c bt u mt ngy sau khi phu thut mch mu v gip thuyn gim hon ton cc triu chng  tt c cc bnh nhn c iu tr ( p &lt; 0,01)</span></li>\n</ul>\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"NHNG LU  QUAN TRNG KHI S DNG VIN UNG NATTO SAFFRON CA M\" tag_name=\"h2\" color=\"#e71e27\" class=\"font-title\"]\n\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Khng dng sn phm Natto Saffron cho i tng l tr em, ph n c thai v ang cho con b. V nguy c lm tan cc mu ng, do , nn ngng s dng trc khi thc hin phu thut.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thn trng khi dng Natto Saffron cho ph n trong giai on hnh kinh, nhng ngi mc tnh trng chm ng mu hoc ang chy mu cp tnh.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngoi ra, cn lu  v cc i tng c nguy c v cc bnh l tim mch lin quan n cc mu ng (nhi mu c tim do to cc mu ng, i tho ng, x va mch, ri lon m mu, tha cn, bo ph) v ngi sau tai bin tc mch  n nh s dng  gip phng nga bnh l lin quan n cc mu ng v tng cng sc khe tim mch.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tnh trng ri lon chy mu: Nattokinase c th lm cho tnh trng ri lon chy mu tr nn ti t hn. Do , cn s dng mt cch cn thn.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tht thn trng khi dng sn phm ny trn i tng huyt p thp.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Lu  khi chun b c phu thut: Nattokinase c th lm tng kh nng chy mu qu nhiu trong hoc sau phu thut. Ngoi ra, sn phm cng c th lm cho huyt p kh kim sot trong qu trnh phu thut. Ngng dng thuc t nht 2 tun trc khi phu thut theo lch trnh.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">iu quan trng nht, sn phm ny l thc phm chc nng, khng phi l thuc. Do , khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.</span></li>\n</ol>\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"CU HI THNG GP\" tag_name=\"h2\" color=\"#e71e27\" class=\"font-title\"]\n\n[accordion]\n\n[accordion-item title=\"1. Dng Thuc NATTO SAFRON cha nattokinase ca M bao lu th c tc dng?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thng thng vic b sung cc loi thc phm chc nng s c hiu qu sau 2-3 thng s dng. Thuc b tim mch Natto saffron l mt sn phm c tc dng h tr ngn nga t qu, c th b sung theo liu trnh t 2-3 thng  t hiu qu cao</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"2. Nn Dng Thuc NATTO SAFRON trc hay sau n cho hiu qu nhanh ?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thuc b tim mch Natto plus saffron ung khi bng i, trc n 30 pht hoc sau n 2 gi.</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"3. Ung Vin NATTO SAFFRON chung vi cc loi thuc khc c khng?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thc phm bo v sc khe h tr tim mch, ngn nga t qu Natto PLus Saffron vi thnh phn nattokinase chit xut t mm u tng ln men v Saffron t nhy hoa ngh ty, vi c tnh an ton v lnh tnh, khng gy kch ng. Nh sn xut cha ghi nhn bt k thng tin no v tng tc thuc gia Natto Extra v cc thuc khc, c th dng chung Natto Plus Saffron vi cc sn phm khc</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"4. B huyt p cao s dng vin ung NATTO SAFFRON cha nattokinase ca M c tt khng ?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thuc b tim mch Natto Plus saffron vi s kt hp t ph gia Natto kinase v Saffron, c tc dng h tr ngn nga t qu, bn cnh  Natto extra cn c tc dng h tr cc bnh l lin quan n cc mu ng nh nhi mu c tim, nhi mu no... ng thi gip bnh n huyt p,tng lu thng mu ln no, h tr gic ng ngon, c th dng cho bnh nhn c bnh l tim mch nh cao huyt p</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"5. B TIM MCH s dng thuc NATTO SAFFRON cha nattokinase ca M c c khng ?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-s