hng mu, t  gim thiu nguy c cc bnh v tim mch v phng nga tai bin, n nh tun hon mu no, ci thin tr nh, b sung nng lng cho c th tnh to, khe khon.</span>\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"5\" align=\"left\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"449\" image_size=\"original\" height=\"100%\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"B HOT CHT THIN NHIN H TR PHNG NGA TAI BIN T QU CA NATTO EXTRA\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"934\"]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"5 U IM VT TRI CA NATTO EXTRA PHNG NGA T QU CA M\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"935\"]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"THNG TIN SN PHM NATTO EXTRA CHNG T QU CA M\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"1.THNH PHN CA VIN UNG NATTO EXTRA CHNG T QU C CHA NATTOKINASE SERRAPEPTASE CA M\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"936\"]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"2.CNG DNG CA VIN UNG NATTO EXTRA CHNG T QU C CHA NATTOKINASE SERRAPEPTASE CA M\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[row style=\"collapse\" width=\"full-width\"]\r\n\r\n[col span=\"7\"]\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">n nh huyt p, h tr thc y lu thng mu</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nattokinase h tr lu thng mu, t  gim thiu nguy c cc bnh v tim mch v h tr phng nga tai bin.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">n nh qu trnh tun hon no, ci thin tr nh v tinh thn th thi cho ngi dng.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">B sung nng lng cho c th tnh to, khe khon</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"5\" align=\"left\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"937\" image_size=\"original\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"VIN UNG NATTO EXTRA CHNG T QU C CHA NATTOKINASE SERRAPEPTASE CA M\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"1.NGUN GC XUT X\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Sn phm nhp khu chnh hng t Hoa K</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nhp khu, phn phi v chu trch nhim v cht lng sn phm:CNG TY C PHN XUT NHP KHU QUC T EU-HMD PHARMA</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Phn phi bi cng ty C phn Dc M Phm HMD PHARMA</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Nh sn xut EARTHS CREATION USA, Hoa K.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"2.I TNG S DNG VIN UNG NATTO EXTRA\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Dng cho ngi trng thnh cn tng cng sc khe tim mch.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngi lu thng mu km, hay b hoa mt chng mt, au u</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngi c nguy c x va ng mch do hm lng cholesterol cao</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngi cn ngn nga t qu, tai bin</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"3.CCH S DNG NATTO EXTRA\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ung 1 vin/ln, ngy ung 1 n 2 ln lc bng i.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"4.BO QUN\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Bo qun ni kh ro</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thong mt trnh nh nng mt tri</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Trnh xa tm tay tr em</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"5.HN S DNG\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hn s dng in trn bao b sn phm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"HIU QU  C KHOA HC CHNG MINH\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"1.T L THAY I MC  LIPID T TUN TH 4 V TUN TH 8 GIA 2 NHM NGHIN CU SO VI BAN U\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"943\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Mc  lipid  tun th 4 v 8 gim khng ng k. Tuy nhin c xu hng gim cholesterol ton phn trong huyt thanh nhiu hn  nhm dng nattokinase (-6,15 v -0,71 tng ng sau 4 tun v -6,8 v +1,94 tng ng sau 8 tun, cng sut = 0,25).</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tng cng c 6 trong s 15 (40) bnh nhn trong nhm iu tr bng nattokinase t c mc cholesterol huyt thanh di 200 mg/dl sau 8 tun(p ng cc tiu ch ca NCEP v EAS).</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">LDL-C cng gim nhiu hn sau 8 tun  nhm nattokinase (-10,85 , -6,3 tng ng)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[title style=\"bold\" text=\"2.S : S THAY I NNG  CHOLESTEROL TON PHN, LDL-C V MC HDL-C.  C HAI NHM CNG CHO THY XU HNG GIM NHIU HN  NHM UNG NATTOKINASE.\" tag_name=\"h4\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"945\"]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[section]\r\n\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"NHNG LU  KHI S DNG VIN UNG NATTO EXTRA CA M\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Khng dng sn phm Natto Extra cho i tng l tr em, ph n c thai v ang cho con b. V nguy c lm tan cc mu ng, do , nn ngng s dng trc khi thc hin phu thut.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thn trng khi dng Natto Extra cho ph n trong giai on hnh kinh, nhng ngi mc tnh trng chm ng mu hoc ang chy mu cp tnh.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Ngoi ra, cn lu  v cc i tng c nguy c v cc bnh l tim mch lin quan n cc mu ng (nhi mu c tim do to cc mu ng, i tho ng, x va mch, ri lon m mu, tha cn, bo ph) v ngi sau tai bin tc mch  n nh s dng  gip phng nga bnh l lin quan n cc mu ng v tng cng sc khe tim mch.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tnh trng ri lon chy mu: Nattokinase c th lm cho tnh trng ri lon chy mu tr nn ti t hn. Do , cn s dng mt cch cn thn.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Tht thn trng khi dng sn phm ny trn i tng huyt p thp.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Lu  khi chun b c phu thut: Nattokinase c th lm tng kh nng chy mu qu nhiu trong hoc sau phu thut. Ngoi ra, sn phm cng c th lm cho huyt p kh kim sot trong qu trnh phu thut. Ngng dng thuc t nht 2 tun trc khi phu thut theo lch trnh.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">iu quan trng nht, sn phm ny l thc phm chc nng, khng phi l thuc. Do , khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/section]\r\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"CU HI THNG GP V NATTO EXTRA\" color=\"#00a651\"]\r\n\r\n[accordion]\r\n\r\n[accordion-item title=\"1. Dng Thuc NATTO EXTRA cha nattokinase ca M bao lu th c tc dng?\"]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thng thng vic b sung cc loi thc phm chc nng s c hiu qu sau 2-3 thng s dng. Thc phm bo v sc khe tim mch Natto extra l mt sn phm c tc dng h tr ngn nga t qu, vi thnh phn c s kt hp t ph t Nattokinase v serrapeptase c th b sung theo liu trnh t 2-3 thng  cho hiu qu cao.</span>\r\n\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n[accordion-item title=\"2. Nn Dng vin ung NATTO EXTRA trc hay sau n cho hiu qu nhanh ?\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">S dng Natto extra cha nattokinase ca M khi bng i trc n 30 pht</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">S dng sau n 2 gi  t hiu qu cao</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n[accordion-item title=\"3. Ung Vi