u  khi chun b c phu thut: Nattokinase c th lm tng kh nng chy mu qu nhiu trong hoc sau phu thut. Ngoi ra, sn phm cng c th lm cho huyt p kh kim sot trong qu trnh phu thut. Ngng dng thuc t nht 2 tun trc khi phu thut theo lch trnh.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">iu quan trng nht, sn phm ny l thc phm chc nng, khng phi l thuc. Do , khng c tc dng thay th thuc cha bnh.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n[/section]\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"CU HI THNG GP V NATTO EXTRA\" color=\"#00a651\"]\n\n[accordion]\n\n[accordion-item title=\"1. Dng Thuc NATTO EXTRA cha nattokinase ca M bao lu th c tc dng?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thng thng vic b sung cc loi thc phm chc nng s c hiu qu sau 2-3 thng s dng. Thc phm bo v sc khe tim mch Natto extra l mt sn phm c tc dng h tr ngn nga t qu, vi thnh phn c s kt hp t ph t Nattokinase v serrapeptase c th b sung theo liu trnh t 2-3 thng  cho hiu qu cao.</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"2. Nn Dng vin ung NATTO EXTRA trc hay sau n cho hiu qu nhanh ?\"]\n\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">S dng Natto extra cha nattokinase ca M khi bng i trc n 30 pht</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">S dng sau n 2 gi  t hiu qu cao</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"3. Ung Vin NATTO EXTRA chung vi cc loi thuc khc c khng?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thc phm bo v sc khe h tr tim mch, ngn nga t qu Natto Extra vi thnh phn nattokinase chit xut t mm u tng ln men v serrapeptase an ton v lnh tnh, khng gy kch ng. Nh sn xut cha ghi nhn bt k thng tin no v tng tc thuc gia Natto Extra v cc thuc khc, c th dng chung Natto Extra vi cc sn phm khc.</span></p>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n[accordion-item title=\"4. B huyt p cao s dng thuc NATTO EXTRA cha nattokinase ca M c tt khng ?\"]\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sa